com.bmc.arsys.api

Class AttachmentPoolField

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bmc.arsys.api.ObjectBase
      • com.bmc.arsys.api.Field
        • com.bmc.arsys.api.AttachmentPoolField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IARPersistentObject, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class AttachmentPoolField
extends Field
implements Serializable
    An attachment pool contains attachment fields that enable users to store text, graphics, audio, or video with a request. Attachment data is compressed and stored in the database with each request.
